Base is built with a commitment to Ethereum’s ethos of decentralization. As an open-source protocol, it invites contributions from the global developer community, ensuring transparency and resilience. While Coinbase plays a central role in its development, Base is designed to align with the broader Web3 community’s values, avoiding the pitfalls of centralized control.This balance of professional stewardship and open-source principles makes Base a trustworthy platform for the long term. Believing in Base means supporting a project that upholds the core ideals of blockchain while delivering practical solutions.

